🌐 Technical
Topic: Computer Networking
1️⃣ Clear Theory (Easy Language)

A Computer Network is a group of computers connected together to share:

Data

Resources

Internet

Devices (printers, servers)

Example:

Office network

Internet

College WiFi network

2️⃣ Types of Computer Networks
🔹 LAN (Local Area Network)

Small area

Example: School, office network

🔹 MAN (Metropolitan Area Network)

Covers a city

🔹 WAN (Wide Area Network)

Covers large area / countries

Example: Internet

3️⃣ Important Network Devices
🔹 Router

Connects different networks.

🔹 Switch

Connects devices in LAN.

🔹 Hub

Basic device that broadcasts data to all devices.

🔹 Modem

Connects computer to internet.

4️⃣ Important Networking Concepts
🔹 IP Address

Unique address of a device on network.

Example:
192.168.1.1

🔹 DNS

Converts domain name → IP address

Example:
google.com → IP address

🔹 HTTP

Protocol used for web browsing.

🧠 Quick Tricks

Internet = Largest WAN

DNS = Domain → IP

Router connects networks

Switch connects devices

